data.description: Bailey Homes popular Aspen model with bonus room over the garage for additional bedroom/family room space. The main floor features the perfect great room area with vaulted ceiling, spacious kitchen with large island and plenty of pantry space,  you can cook and easily talk to your guests! You will find beautiful granite counter tops, and upgraded cabinets throughout this home. This beautiful  home still feels like new inside and has been up-kept incredibly well!
